      "comment": "POPPYONTHEBEACH (9) has been in the placings two times from as many runs this campaign. Went well again last time over 2100m at Bunbury, finishing second and a neck from the winner. Will need a bit of luck negotiating a very wide starting position but rates a primary contender based on those recent efforts. QUEEN OF ALL (6) was yet again about the mark last start when runner-up over 1730m at this track, beaten 8 metres. Meets a comparable field and she can go one better without surprising. MARGIMAC (3) disappointed last time when tenth over 2130m here. Can atone from the low draw. ALFA JESS (11) is in the mix at her first run since finishing fourth over 2030m at Busselton five months ago. Can run a race while fresh.",
